4.1 Chính sách đình chỉ đối với Đơn hàng.source_string: 4.1 Suspension Policy for Wish Express Orders

4.1.1 Chính sách Đình chỉ theo dõi các đ.source_string: 4.1.1 The Suspension Policy measures Wish Express orders weekly, from Monday through Sunday.

4.1.2 Tài khoản người bán sẽ bị đình chỉ.source_string: 4.1.2 A merchant account will be suspended from Wish Express in the destination countries where its On-Time Arrival Rate is under 90% and/or the Pre-Fulfillment Cancellation Rate is ≥ 10% for the most recent measurement period. In both situations, merchants will receive an infraction warning on the suspension. Merchants may file disputes in response to the suspension within 11 calendar days from receiving the infraction details.

4.1.3 Nếu trước đó tài khoản người bán đ.source_string: 4.1.3 If a merchant account has previously been suspended three times by the Suspension Policy for U.S. Wish Express, or five times for non-U.S. Wish Express, the merchant account will be permanently removed from Wish Express in the corresponding country/countries.

4.1.4 Chính sách này sẽ được thực thi ở.source_string: 4.1.4 The policy will be executed on a per-country level. Merchants will apply to and/or be suspended for each Wish Express destination country individually.

4.1.5 Người bán có thể đăng ký lại Wish.source_string: 4.1.5 Merchant can re-apply for Wish Express immediately after suspension, unless they exceed the allowed number of suspensions

4.2 Chính sách phạt đối với Đơn hàng Wis.source_string: 4.2 Penalties Policy for Non-Compliant Wish Express orders

4.2.1 Tất cả các đơn hàng của Wish Expre.source_string: 4.2.1 All Wish Express orders that are not confirmed delivered by carriers before the end of the fifth working day after the on-time delivery requirement from order released date will not be eligible for payment.

4.2.2 Chính sách phạt đánh giá các đơn h.source_string: 4.2.2 The Penalties Policy measures Wish Express orders weekly, from Monday through Sunday. Late delivery orders will be penalized by {%1=Example: 20%} of the order value or {%2=Format Currency}, whichever is greater. For confirmed shipped US orders, a flat exemption of {%3=Example: 1%} Wish Express Total Order Value will be applied. For the confirmed shipped orders to the rest of the countries, a flat exemption of {%4=Example: 2%} of Wish Express Total Order Value will be applied and calculated on a per-country basis. Merchants will be subject to Late Confirmed Fulfillment Policy 5.5 and penalized for all orders not confirmed shipped by carrier within 168 hours. Note that this policy is only applicable to confirmed fulfilled orders where the merchant price per item plus the shipping price per item is less than {%5=Format Currency}; the penalty is reversible upon confirmed delivery by the carrier within required Wish Express delivery time frame. Cookie và Công nghệ có Liên quan - Chúng.source_string: Cookies and Related Technologies - We and others may use cookies, which are text files containing small amounts of information that are downloaded on your device, or related technologies, such as web beacons, local shared objects and tracking pixels to store or collect information ("Cookies"). Cookies can help us and others learn about your online activity including on other sites or services. For example, web beacons allow ad networks to provide aggregated auditing, research and reporting for us and for advertisers. Web beacons also enable ad networks to serve targeted advertisements to you when you visit other websites. Because your web browser must request these advertisements and web beacons from the ad network's servers, these companies can view, edit, or set their own cookies, just as if you had requested a web page from their site.

All orders, including Wish Express orders, are also subject to the [Merchant Policy 5.5 - Late Confirmed Fulfillment Policy]({%3=Example: #5.5}), which states that if an order is not confirmed shipped by the carrier within {%4=A number, e.g. 168} hours of the time the order is released, then the merchant will be penalized {%5=A number, e.g. 20}% of the order value, or {%6=Fine USD Amount}, whichever is greater. This policy is only applicable to confirmed fulfilled orders where (merchant price per item + shipping price per item) is less than {%7=Fine USD Amount}. Phụ lục 2: Có hiệu lực vào ngày 6 tháng.source_string: Addendum 2: Effective August 6, 2019 8PM Pacific Time, if a product listing or a product variation is detected to be misleading, the merchant may be penalized up to {%1=Format Currency}* if there were orders placed in the last {%2=A number, e.g. 30} days from when the product or variation was detected as misleading. Merchants may also be responsible for {%3=A number, e.g. 100}% of any future refund on an order placed on the detected misleading product or variation.

Phụ lục ProductBoost này (sau đây gọi là.source_string: This ProductBoost Addendum (the "Addendum") contains the terms and conditions that govern your access to and use of various services relating to the advertising and promotion of your products and/or brand (collectively, the "ProductBoost Services") on the website(s), services or applications, including, without limitation, the website at [{%1=Wish Main URL}]({%2=Wish Main URL}) and app offered under the name Wish, and the websites and apps offered by us, including without limitation under the names Geek, Cute, Home, and Mama (collectively, the “Services”), offered by ContextLogic Inc. (collectively, “Wish,” “we,” or is”). This Addendum modifies and supplements the existing Merchant Terms of Services agreement between you and Wish, which currently is available at [the “Terms”]({%3=Merchant Terms Of Service}).

Phụ lục: Các đơn hàng của Chương trình h.source_string: Addendum: Advanced Logistics Program orders that are removed by merchants from the program and allowed to be shipped from warehouses outside of Mainland China must be fulfilled with a [Qualified Confirmed Delivery Shipping Carrier]({%1=Example: /documentation/v2/qualifiedcarr}).

Phụ lục: Có hiệu lực từ ngày 15 tháng 8.source_string: Addendum: Effective August 15, 2018 00:00 UTC, the merchant will also be penalized {%1=Format Currency}* per auto-refunded order in this case.

Phụ lục: Có hiệu lực từ ngày 20 tháng 3.source_string: Addendum: Effective March 20, 2019 00:00 UTC, if a product variation is detected to be misleading, the variation will be removed from the product, and the merchant will be penalized {%1=Format Currency}* per misleading variation order and {%2=A number, e.g. 100}% of the order value for orders placed in the last {%3=A number, e.g. 30} days from when the particular product variation was detected as misleading, with a minimum penalty of {%4=Format Currency}* per detected misleading product variation.

Phụ lục: Có hiệu lực từ ngày 23 tháng 7.source_string: Addendum: Effective July 23, 2019, the penalty will not be reversed if the merchant updates the tracking number for any reason.

Phụ lục: Có hiệu lực từ ngày 6 tháng 11.source_string: Addendum: Effective November 6, 2019 00:00 Beijing Time, merchants may dispute the additional fee only via the EPC Dispute Tool within their WishPost account.

Phụ lục: Có hiệu lực từ ngày 6 tháng 8 n.source_string: Addendum: Effective August 6, 2019 8PM Pacific Time, if a merchant changes a product listing into a new product, the product will be removed, the account will be penalized up to {%1=Format Currency}*, and the account will be at risk of suspension.

Addendum: Effective August 6, 2019 8PM Pacific Time, upon review for counterfeit and intellectual property infringement, if a product is found to violate Wish's policy, it will be removed and all payments will be withheld, and the merchant may be penalized up to {%1=Format Currency}* per counterfeit product.

Addendum: Effective August 6, 2019 8PM Pacific Time, if a product listing is detected to not comply with Wish’s prohibited product listing policies, the merchant will be penalized up to {%1=Format Currency}* and the product listing will be taken down.

Phụ lục: Có hiệu lực vào ngày 31 tháng 1.source_string: Addendum: Effective October 31, 2018 5PM Pacific Time, merchants are allowed to dispute these penalties within {%1=A number, e.g. 3} business days after a penalty statement is generated.

Phụ lục: Có hiệu lực vào ngày 6 tháng 8.source_string: Addendum: Effective August 6, 2019 8PM Pacific Time, if a store disables or removes a promoted product with {%1=Format Currency}+ GMV* in the last {%2=A number, e.g. 9} days, or if a store disables a specific country for a promoted product with {%3=Format Currency}+ GMV* in the last {%4=A number, e.g. 9} days in that country, the store will be penalized {%5=Format Currency}*.

Addendum: Effective August 6, 2019 8PM Pacific Time, orders that are found to have been affected by manipulated reviews and/or ratings are subject to be penalized up to {%1=Format Currency}* per affected order.

Phụ lục: Người bán chỉ có thể gỡ đơn hàn.source_string: Addendum: Merchants may only remove an Advanced Logistics Program order from the program for one of the qualified reasons. Order removal found to be based on non-qualified reasons may be penalized {%1=Format Currency}* per noncompliant order. Repeated violations of this policy may be subject to further penalties such as account suspension.

Phụ lục: Người bán chỉ có thể xóa đơn hà.source_string: Addendum: Merchants may only remove an Advanced Logistics Program order from the program for one of the reasons stated within this policy.

Please note that other Wish Merchant Pol.source_string: Please note that other Wish Merchant Policies also may cover products in-scope of this policy but for other regions (e.g., Regionally Restricted Items Policy, Hazardous Materials Policy, Weapon Policy, Dangerous/Unsafe Items Policy, etc.).
